assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Alkaline Fuel Cell Power Corp. designs, develops, produces, and commercializes micro combined heat and power systems based on alkaline fuel cell technology for residential, industrial, and commercial markets worldwide. The company was formerly known as Black Isle Resources Corp. and changed its name to Alkaline Fuel Cell Power Corp. in June 2021. Alkaline Fuel Cell Power Corp. was incorporated in 1987 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
